Text: FEA to present ENERGYStorage at Houston conferenceFEA will be presenting at Infocasts Gas Valuation and Storage conference in Houston TX USA Tuesday October th pmpm FEA Financial Engineer King Wang PhD will present FEA ENERGYStorage Software for Gas Storage Valuation and Optimization Visit gasvolhtm for more information Please let me know if you would like to schedule a private demonstration of the FEA ENERGYStorage model Dr Wang and I look forward to seeing you in Houston Nicole Kraiza FEA Sales Consultant x
